title: Fear Of Letting People Down
description:
Sadie is joined on the podcast by television personality and author Elisabeth Hasselbeck. Elisabeth is known from her roles on Survivor, The View, and FOX & Friends. She shares advice her dad gave her about the fear of letting people down and how her father’s love helped her understand how God sees her.
